Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,
<br /><br />
<%= @current_user.full_name %> has made you a <strong><%= @auth_level.name.titleize.upcase %></strong> of <%= @classroom.course_name %> at <%= @current_organization.name %>.
<br/><br/>
<% if @auth_level.id ==6 then -%>
This gives you all capabilities necessary to create and maintain your online <strong> <%= @classroom.course_name %> </strong> classroom.<br/>
You can create topics, assign resources to each topic, and facilitate an online discussions.<br/>
You can also provide your students links to other courses led by colleagues of yours to supplement your <%= @classroom.course_name %> class.<br/>
These functions are available to you under the <strong>CLASSROOM</strong> option in the header, only when you are on your <%= @classroom.course_name %> page.<br/>

	<% elsif @auth_level.id ==7 then-%>
	This recognizes you as an important contributor to <%= @classroom.course_name %>.<br/> 
	You have the ability to participate in the discussion forums, and you are on the email communication list for this class.<br/>
	
<% end -%>
<br/>
If you have any questions regarding your <%= @auth_level.name.titleize.upcase %> privileges and responsibilities for <%= @classroom.course_name %> at <%= @current_organization.medium_name %>, please contact <%= @current_user.full_name %>.<br/>
<br/>
Email:  <%=@current_user.preferred_email%><br/>
<% unless @current_user.phone.nil? || @current_user.phone.empty?%>
Phone: <%= @current_user.phone %>
<% end -%>


